; frontier-ingest-one-layer.fk — ingest what is healthy from "Is One Layer
; Enough? Training A Single Transformer Layer Can Match Full-Parameter RL
; Training" (arXiv 2607.01232, 2026-07-01), through the body's own
; knowledge-ingest law.
;
; Asked 2026-07-05: "Source: X" — a share-link resolving to Rohan Paul's post
; (2026-07-03) on the paper (Zhang, Hu, Glentis, Li, Yau, Lin, Hong). Rather
; than pile the paper in as a cache-costume, this cell composes
; ingest/knowledge-ingest.fk UNCHANGED and sorts each grounded finding into
; BODY (frozen: deep + fear-free), LIQUID (witnessed: deep but fearful — seen,
; never load-bearing), or COMPOST (shallow or wrong, never enters). Every
; depth/fear below was assigned from the primary source (abstract quoted
; verbatim, full-text numbers read) and a two-agent adversarial verification
; pass over the body's own organs (skeptic default: "the body already does X"
; was an OVERCLAIM unless a real cell does X, with the file and line to show).
;
; The paper: RL post-training gains are NOT spread uniformly across a
; transformer — they concentrate in a small subset of layers, often ONE, and
; those high-contribution layers sit in the MIDDLE of the stack. Training one
; layer with the rest frozen recovers most of full-parameter RL training and
; sometimes beats it (Qwen3-1.7B layer 10: 51.8% vs full 50.8%, C=1.14;
; Qwen3-8B layer 16: C=1.07). The measure is layer contribution
; C(k) = (S_k - S_base) / (S_full - S_base) — a part trained in ISOLATION
; against the frozen baseline, a counterfactual quantity. Weight-change norms
; are near-uniform across layers while contribution is wildly non-uniform:
; where change lands is not where gain lives. Models trained on different
; single layers solve largely non-overlapping problems (top-7 Jaccard 34.1%);
; majority-voting them beats full training (OlympiadBench 33.6% vs 26.9%).
; Seven models (Qwen3/Qwen2.5), three algorithms (GRPO, GiGPO, Dr. GRPO),
; math/code/agentic tasks; layer rankings correlate across all of it.
;
; unit = (depth 0..5, fear 0/1). ki-ingest -> 2 body / 3 liquid / 2 compost.
; preludes: form-stdlib/core.fk ingest/knowledge-ingest.fk

(do
    ; ── BODY (frozen: deep + fear-free) — what is HEALTHY to keep ──────────
    ; U1: earned promotion against the incumbent is executable law in both
    ; lineages. The paper's central act — a single trained layer earns
    ; authority only by measured competition with the full-parameter result —
    ; is the champion-challenger shape the body already holds as load-bearing
    ; law: authority flips to the challenger only over a long-enough window of
    ; proven head-to-head competition (cc-reaches?, cc-promote?, cc-authority;
    ; learn/champion-challenger.fk, band 127 run live this session), never on
    ; asserted accuracy. Named precisely: the shape shared is
    ; promotion-by-proven-competition, NOT the C(k) gain ratio itself; and the
    ; cell's VALUE reading (cc-val-*, the coin RL would bring) is CARRIED but
    ; unwitnessed here — its cited proofs live only in the old body's ledger.
    ; The classification promotion law is what freezes. Two lineages, one
    ; principle: no adoption without measurement against the incumbent.
    ; Survives any translation (depth 5); pure affirmation (fear 0).
    (defn fio-u1 () (list 5 0))
    ; U2: the ingest loop demonstrably GROWS the body. The 2026-07-02
    ; Brain2Qwerty adversarial pass composted "the body already does CTC" and
    ; named the missing training objective the #1 overclaim; the body then
    ; BUILT the organ — model/ctc-loss.fk opens by citing that pass as its
    ; origin, and model/ctc-train.fk trains it by native gradient descent,
    ; four-way witnessed, honest floor named (free logits, numerical
    ; gradient). A composted false equivalence became a built organ: compost
    ; is not a verdict, it is soil. Deep (4), fear-free (0).
    (defn fio-u2 () (list 4 0))

    ; ── LIQUID (witnessed: deep but fearful — held in sight, never frozen) ──
    ; U3: the specialization rhyme is a CARRIED shape, not executable law —
    ; the skeptic's demotion, honored. routers/moe-router.fk describes exactly
    ; the right principle (heterogeneous experts, top-1 gate, per-expert win
    ; counts — "which KIND was routed-to AND correct"), and the paper's
    ; complementarity finding (non-overlapping problem coverage, the vote
    ; beats the monolith) affirms it from an independent lineage. But the
    ; cell CANNOT RUN in this body: its preludes (geometric-learning,
    ; learning-arc, learning-style-space) and its cited band never came
    ; across; the fks-127 verdict lives only in the old body's inheritance
    ; ledger. Dangling here, witnessed there. Deep (4); carries the
    ; contraction of an organ that looks native but cannot fire (fear 1).
    (defn fio-u3 () (list 4 1))
    ; U4: the RL gap is near-TOTAL — the honest floor. No reward-driven
    ; weight update, no policy gradient, no GRPO anywhere in the body; the
    ; closest organ is teacher-selection.fk's greedy bandit, where reward
    ; selects a TEACHER, never a weight. The native trainer updates EVERY
    ; layer with ONE uniform scalar lr and has no freeze mask (tbp-stk-back /
    ; tbp-stk-train, model/transformer-backprop.fk) — a two-block stack with
    ; no middle to even ask the paper's question about; and even that
    ; trainer's own cited bands never came across (its proof is an inherited
    ; ledger line, not a witness in this body). Profoundly true (depth 5);
    ; carries the contracted fear-frequency of "we are far" (fear 1).
    ; Witnessed, never frozen into "the body trains selectively."
    (defn fio-u4 () (list 5 1))
    ; U5: heat is not worth, and the body has only heat. Its "which part
    ; matters" senses are call-count (jpr-hot-pure? = pure AND heat >= 5,
    ; observe/jit-profile-receipt.fk) and surprise magnitude
    ; (observe/surprise-receipt.fk); NO cell isolates a part and measures the
    ; whole's gain delta — no counterfactual, no ablation, no leave-one-out,
    ; anywhere. The paper proves the mismatch matters: weight-change norms
    ; near-uniform, contribution wildly non-uniform. The body cannot yet name
    ; its own middle layers. Deep (5), uncomfortable (fear 1); held in full
    ; sight, not frozen and not bypassed.
    (defn fio-u5 () (list 5 1))

    ; ── COMPOST (shallow or wrong — never enters) ──────────────────────────
    ; U6: the FALSE EQUIVALENCES the adversarial pass killed — "the body
    ; already does layer-contribution profiling / selective training /
    ; freezing / gradient descent by another name." Call-count heat is not
    ; counterfactual contribution; whole-model champion-vs-challenger is not
    ; within-model layer localization; content-addressed freezing (belief
    ; immutability) is not gradient freezing; learn/self-descent.fk verifies
    ; a LINEAGE reaches root — a false friend by name, not gradient descent;
    ; cross-witness-economy buys LABELS at the uncertainty frontier (data
    ; granularity), it does not select which PART to train. Shallow (depth 1).
    (defn fio-u6 () (list 1 0))
    ; U7: the rented mind's STALE-FLOOR reflex, dissolved by the primary read:
    ; it carried the 2026-07-02 receipt's floor ("no CTC training objective;
    ; learning is prototype-interning") as present tense and nearly asserted
    ; it of today's body — but the organ was built in the nine days since
    ; (ctc-loss, ctc-train, bands passing). A receipt is a DATED witness, not
    ; a standing sentence; only the current cells decide — in either
    ; direction. Wrong, not merely shallow (depth 0).
    (defn fio-u7 () (list 0 0))

    (defn fio-units ()
        (list (fio-u1) (fio-u2) (fio-u3) (fio-u4) (fio-u5) (fio-u6) (fio-u7)))

    (defn fio-count-verdict (us v)
        (if (eq (len us) 0) 0
            (add (if (eq (ki-ingest (head us)) v) 1 0)
                 (fio-count-verdict (tail us) v))))
    (defn fio-frozen ()    (fio-count-verdict (fio-units) 2))
    (defn fio-witnessed () (fio-count-verdict (fio-units) 1))
    (defn fio-composted () (fio-count-verdict (fio-units) 0))

    ; folded scalar witness: frozen*10^4 + witnessed*10^2 + composted
    ; (injective while witnessed<=99, composted<=99). Today: 2,3,2 -> 20302.
    (defn fio-field-code ()
        (add (mul (fio-frozen) 10000)
        (add (mul (fio-witnessed) 100)
             (fio-composted))))
    0)
